Let me think for a minute.

379
00:23:14,073 --> 00:23:15,665
What are you gonna do?

380
00:23:15,708 --> 00:23:18,074
Come on. I got an idea.

381
00:23:18,110 --> 00:23:19,077
Did you get
everything you want?

382
00:23:19,111 --> 00:23:21,807
I got the Latin
and the Sanskrit...

383
00:23:21,847 --> 00:23:23,474
