402
00:24:28,848 --> 00:24:30,315
God, you look great.

403
00:24:30,349 --> 00:24:32,943
Thanks. Are you taking
astronomy, too?

404
00:24:32,985 --> 00:24:34,885
Yeah, I guess so.

405
00:24:34,920 --> 00:24:36,979
