then we'd reconsider...

419
00:25:09,121 --> 00:25:10,918
but until that day,
take a hike...

420
00:25:10,956 --> 00:25:14,050
you elitist fraternity scumbag.

421
00:25:17,730 --> 00:25:19,789
I won't forget this, Melon.

422
00:25:19,832 --> 00:25:21,595
