431
00:25:52,097 --> 00:25:53,792
All I know is I'm supposed
to pick him up here.

432
00:25:53,832 --> 00:25:55,800
- When?
- Now.

433
00:25:55,834 --> 00:25:58,530
Come on, let's register.

434
00:26:07,212 --> 00:26:08,736
