tomorrow at 11:00.

470
00:27:50,849 --> 00:27:52,009
11:00? No good.

471
00:27:52,051 --> 00:27:54,212
I got a massage at 11:00.
Tell them to make it 2:00.

472
00:27:54,253 --> 00:27:57,416
No, Dad, you don't get it.

473
00:27:57,456 --> 00:28:01,586
